headline.print_headline: Goffin Wins 2nd Career Title at Moselle Open
headline.main: Goffin Wins 2nd Career Title at Moselle Open

lead_paragraph: Eighth-seeded David Goffin of Belgium served 10 aces and saved all four break points he faced to claim his second career title with a 6-4, 6-3 win over Joao Sousa of Portugal in the Moselle Open final on Sunday.
